{"tid":2514112,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝有個同事冇閂窗搞到公司水浸，比老細屌到痴咗線。。。","createTime":"2021-05-03T05:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:25:04.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6874817e6421255f9e28d6c20b42281a0e08d073","tid":2514112,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"大家都知今日落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個同事走咗出去先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔記得閂窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就搞到公司水浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個老細就捉住呢樣野狂屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又無啦啦拉埋佢平時做野黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話佢無撚用呀，話佢直播冇準備要罰錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌咗十幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個同事應該係俾佢屌到跳咗制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦開始拍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住拍手個咇開始唱唱好泰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「昨天阿媽 姑媽兼阿嫂 問起我泰國能去嗎？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「沙惑dee club lee 悶娣 Yim Hi 堪慣豔dee」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老細嚇撚到呆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咗句你都痴撚線就返房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家個同事仲係到唱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95584baf4a5508d0f2d123a6d6a78fb94009a443","tid":2514112,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma